;More choices for your New Tab
Barrachd roghainnean dhan taba ùr agad


;The New Tab page offers convenience and more control of your browsing experience.
Tha duilleag nan tabaichean ùra goireasach is a’ toirt dhut barrachd smachd air a’ bhrabhsadh a nì thu.


;Turn on Suggested Sites for a personalized experience of frequently used sites and relevant recommendations every time you open a New Tab.
Cuir air molaidhean làraichean airson ’s gum faic thu làraichean air am bi thu gu tric is molaidhean iomchaidh gach turas a dh’fhosglas tu taba ùr.


;Personalize your New Tab experience
Cuir dreach pearsanta air gleus nan tabaichean ùra


;You are in complete control of your New Tab page.
’S ann agad-sa a tha làn-smachd air duilleag nan tabaichean ùra.


;Customize your experience by rearranging, pinning or removing sites, and set up New Tab just the way you want it.
Cuir dreach pearsanta air rudan le bhith a’ gluasadh làraichean mun cuairt, ’gam prìneachadh no toirt air falbh agus suidhich gleus nan tabaichean ùra dìreach a-rèir do thoil fhèin.


;Drag a site to exactly where you want it.
Slaod làrach dìreach far a bheil thu ’ga iarraidh.


;Once you’ve found the perfect spot for your site, pin it to make it stay.
Turas a lorg thu an t-àite ceart dhan làrach agad, prìnich e gus a chumail ann.


;Make a site disappear by deleting it from your New Tab page.
Sguab làrach à duilleag nan tabaichean ùra gus a thoirt air falbh.


;Learn more about customizing New Tab Page
Barrachd fiosrachaidh mu ghnàthachadh duilleag nan tabaichean ùra


;Discover new sites and content on the Web
Lorg làraichean is susbaint ùr air an lìon


;If enabled, Firefox displays website links as thumbnails (miniaturized images) or logos on your New Tab page. These are called Tiles.
Ma bhios e an comas, nochdaidh Firefox ceanglaichean ri làraichean-lìn mar dhealbhagan no suaicheantasan air duilleag nan tabaichean ùra agad. ’S e leacagan a chanar riutha.


;Tiles save you time by giving you quick access to your frequently visited sites, as well as showing new sites and content that are similar to sites you already love. Here are the types of Tiles you may see:
Sàbhailidh tu ùine leis na leacagan is iad ’gad thoirt gu àitichean air an tadhal thu gu tric gu luath agus seallaidh iad làraichean is susbaint ùr dhut a tha coltach ri stuth a tha a’ còrdadh riut mu thràth. Seo nàdar nan leacagan a chì thu:


;Top sites
Brod nan làrach


;New Tab will show the “top sites” you visited most recently and frequently, so you can access them quickly.
Chì thu brod nan làrach air an do thadhail thu gus tric is o chionn goirid ann an gleus nan tabaichean ùra ach am faigh thu greim orra gu luath.


;Suggested sites
Làraichean a mholamaid


;See sites and content suggested to you based on categories that Firefox matches to your browsing history.
Faic làraichean is susbaint a-rèir na h-eachdraidh brabhsaidh agad ann am Firefox.


;They will be clearly labeled in your New Tab as “Suggested,” or when the suggestion is from a commercial partner, they will be labeled as “Sponsored,” and will indicate the identified interest category.
Tha iad furasta ri an aithneachadh ann an gleus nan tabaichean ùra is “Moladh” riutha no mas ann o chom-pàirtiche malairteach a tha e, bidh comharra “Sponsairichte” riutha agus nochdaidh iad na diofar roinnean sa bheil iad.


;If you’re getting started
Mas e toiseach-tòiseachaidh a tha thu a’ dèanamh


;If you’re using Firefox for the first time, the New Tab page is already populated with useful and interesting sites and content.
Ma tha thu a’ cleachdadh Firefox a’ chiad turas, chì thu cuid a làraichean is susbaint ann an gleus nan tabaichean ùra mu thràth a dh’fhaodadh a bhith gu feum dhut.


;This includes both referrals to sponsored sites from commercial partners, labeled as “Sponsored,” and content we consider important to our mission of advancing the public benefit of the Internet.
Tha seo a’ gabhail a-staigh ceanglaichean ri làraichean nan com-pàirtichean malairteach againn (is comharra “Sponsairichte” riutha) agus susbaint a tha co-cheangailte ri ar misean – leasachadh an lìn a chum leas a’ phobaill.


;Personalization with your privacy in mind
Pearsantachadh ach le aire dha do phrìobhaideachd


;Mozilla promotes a transparent exchange between users and content providers to make the Web enjoyable and sustainable.
Tha Mozilla a’ brosnachadh eadar-ghabhail shoilleir eadar an luchd-cleachdaidh is solaraichean susbaint airson ’s gum bi an lìon an dà chuir tlachdmhor is so-sheasmhach.


;If suggestions are enabled, Firefox will make suggestions to you based on categories matched to your browsing history and will let you know every time why you are seeing specific suggestions.
Ma bhios na molaidhean an comas, molaidh Firefox rudan dhut a-rèir na h-eachdraidh brabhsaidh agad agus innsidh e dhut gach turas a chì thu moladh sònraichte.


;In delivering Suggested sites, Firefox does not share your personal data, nor place cookies on your computer.
Cha cho-roinn Firefox an dàta pearsanta agad is e a’ toirt dhut làraichean a mholamaid agus cha chuir e briosgaidean air a’ choimpiutair agad.


;Content providers will only receive aggregated information about interactions users have with their tiles.
Chan fhaigh solaraichean susbaint ach fiosrachadh giorraichte air na nì an luchd-cleachdaidh leis na leacagan aca.


;You remain in control of your browsing history, and you can disable recommendations whenever you choose.
’S ann agad-sa a bhios smachd air an eachdraidh bhrabhsaidh agad fad na h-ùine agus is urrainn dhut na molaidhean a chur à comas uair sam bith.


